headline: Deutsche Bank resumes coverage of Intel
summary: Investing.com -- Deutsche Bank resumed coverage of Intel (NASDAQ:INTC) with a Hold rating and a price target of $23 in a note Wednesday, noting cautious optimism about the company’s long-term potential under new CEO Lip-Bu Tan, while warning that a meaningful turnaround will take time.

headline: Where Will Nvidia Be in 3 Years?
summary: Nvidia has a strong edge in AI processors, and complementary strengths in software will make it hard for competitors to catch up.
